{"tid":1536032,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【鳩噏一下】有心整理下毛語錄去嚇下班大陸人","createTime":"2019-09-03T14:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T14:41:42.000Z","uid":312466,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a30027fe263e4f66ad178f2606b14ed516f9a83d","tid":1536032,"uid":312466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:24:30.000Z","msg":"可能之前都有人提過下<br />\n小生發夢不如認真整理下毛語錄嗰啲<br />\n啲nds之類成鬼日嚟搞事<br />\n實行用佢哋崇拜嘅思考打倒返佢哋<br />\n行唔行得通呢<br />\n啲乜鬼&ldquo;哪裏有壓迫，哪裏就有反抗。&rdquo;、&ldquo;沒有調查就沒有發言權&rdquo;嗰啲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"081b5869f0a84f5ec94c6b89507be9d8a838910d","tid":1536032,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:25:01.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"acbef67bf41245918321b55fda033b214abb108c","tid":1536032,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:26:20.000Z","msg":"攞中國國旗嚇佢得㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4cb0511f95edec1ca3fcff2385c03c4b9ac0abf","tid":1536032,"uid":312466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acbef67bf41245918321b55fda033b214abb108c","tid":1536032,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:26:20.000Z","msg":"攞中國國旗嚇佢得㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:31:02.000Z","msg":"要用毛語錄呀<br />\n因為佢哋崇拜嘅毛主席講嘅理論，佢哋邊敢駁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n國旗佢仲可以搬一堆家仇國恥出嚟講，話你唔愛國乜乜乜<br />\n連毛語錄都叫人反抗、造反、調查<br />\n佢哋就詞窮喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（雖然佢哋一早就詞窮咗仲死撐"},{"pid":"918b0eb8453cf2c39da45bcaa51f287a6fdf9114","tid":1536032,"uid":312466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:32:21.000Z","msg":"沒有調查就沒有發言權<br />\n呢句已經嚇死佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a0122489b7a2e1a4506769be7286da501f2d3e2","tid":1536032,"uid":312466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acbef67bf41245918321b55fda033b214abb108c","tid":1536032,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:26:20.000Z","msg":"攞中國國旗嚇佢得㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:41:42.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;群眾是真正的英雄&rdquo;<br />\n其實真係句句都玩死五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}